  <brief_title>Macronutrient Relations and Weight Loss in Obese Subjects</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Macronutrient Relations on Body Weight, Body Composition, and Cardiovascular Risk Markers in Overweight Patients Attending a Telemedically Guided Weight Loss Program</official_title>
  <sponsors>
